This program is an implementatin of the classic "Space Invaders" game from 1978.
It is using Tsdl for graphical output and UI. The images come from a .BMP (RGB, 8 bit per channel) format.

Install SDL2 library (https://www.libsdl.org/) for your system first.

To install Tsdl package:
    opam install tsdl

To build:
    make

To use:
    ./main

Controls: 

Left Arrow Key / A to move Left
Right Arrow Key / D to move Right
Spacebar to shoot 

`Esc` or `Q`: exit
